      <p>MBA P rogramme caters to the continuing educational needs of the Working / Employed professionals in the government, public and private sector who want to assume higher responsibilities to better serve the industry and the society. At present following 2 years MBA (Weekend) courses with myriad specialisations are being offered by USMS - </p>
